snippet.textDisplay: I get goosebumps from the moment Javed Bashir starts... It's just that magical! Masooma's vocals, although unconventional, do every bit a justice to the composition. And those lyrics... I don't think I've heard anything as meaningful in recent times! Faakhir Mehmood impressed us as a singer, earlier this season... He takes away the medal with his music direction too :)
